        <Parent_String>yarn winders [300433380], winders (textileworking tools) [300023533], textile working equipment [300163224], equipment by material processed [300168082], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
